cu.explanation_en: Setting the second integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia10' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the maximum MIMO layers to an out-of-range value '99' will cause configuration validation failure and prevent the DU from initializing properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將最大 MIMO 層數設定為超出範圍的值 '99' 會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止 DU 正確初始化。
